The All Progressives Congress (APC) Caretaker Chairman in Osun State, Gboyega Famoodun, has said that the National Leader of the party, Bola Ahmed Tinubu, is qualified to contest the highest political office in the country. He urged people in the South-West to  work in unity to support the political ambition of Tinubu if he declares his interest to run for the office of president in 2023. The APC chieftain said that Tinubu deserves the support of members of the party owing to the contributions he made for the enthronement of the party at both the national and state levels. To enable commenting and other interactive features, please switch to the more advanced .